{"tid":1522280,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教你用telegram bot報平安","createTime":"2019-08-31T12:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:07:49.000Z","uid":39297,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c3fe52fa23ecb581aba76531685ecf52e16160","tid":1522280,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"話說我朋友個朋友見大家呢排成日都要報平安，所以就寫左個telegram bot<br />\n個bot可以自動隔一陣問下你有冇事 <br />\n如果報出咗事or一段時間內冇回既話就自動會通知你個fd<br />\n唔講咁多比link先: <a href=\"http://t.me/hk_stand_by_me_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk_stand_by_me_bot&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIuzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=59e09708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hk_stand_by_me_bot</a><br />\n用法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n第一步: 搵你個friend 入去條link <br />\n第二步: /start <br />\n個bot會同你介紹下詳細用法<br />\n第三步: /setcontact &lt;打佢個username落黎＞(e.g. /setcontact @standwithhongkong)<br />\n會有驗證碼send比你朋友 要搵你朋友攞番個驗證碼 之後入番落個bot <br />\n第四步: /dream (default 係15分鐘問1次 如果想變可以咁入: /dream 30 咁就會每30分鐘問1次)<br />\n發完夢: /wake<br />\n<br />\n高級玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\nSet完contact 打/register 就可以set幾題security questions, 報平安個陣要答岩先得 等冇人可以假冒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果答錯咗就自動會通知你個fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bb525272ba9d6a42b2ae9b30e9dbe0cdc6998d","tid":1522280,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"304b4080f53d20c8bf4de8a90ad5a0407af0c55b","tid":1522280,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc8282319a9dc9163a1535230871e3438ace79","tid":1522280,"uid":282569